reviewText:
P-Body and Atlas have 5 letters ;
Chell has 5 letters too , coincidence? i didn't thought so ;
14 of my friends have this game , you know what else  has the number 14?
That right!
14 is the atomic number for silicon;
silicon has 7 letters ;
7-5 = 2 ;
Portal 2 is the second game of the Portal series;
Portal was the first;
1+2 = 3
PORTAL 3 CONFIRMED

From the developers of the game that made you forget where you stored your life!Comes a game about puzzle solving at it's best, that will make you lose another countless hours, trying to solve the hardest puzzles, starring:
-A mute female main character;
-A robot that tries to kill you;
-Another robot that tries to kill you, but we like that one;
-A blue portal;
-An orange portal;
-A robot that looks like a football;
-A robot that looks like a soccer ball;
-And much! MUCH! Sarcasm; (cut to GLaDOS saying This is the Computer Intelligence Training and Enrichment Center Human Test Subject Research Center or CInTECH. But why don't we all just agree to call it the hub?")
-(shows the game's cover art and the price below);"
